Custom MCP-Style Tool: analyze_student_load
Tool Name

analyze_student_load

Purpose

analyze_student_load is a custom MCP-style workload analysis tool created for RecoveryPilot.

Its purpose is to analyze a student’s academic workload and return structured facts that the LLM can use to choose a recovery strategy.

Tool Location

Tool logic:

src/mcp/analyzeStudentLoad.ts

Tool schema:

src/mcp/mcpToolDefinitions.ts

LLM wiring:

src/agents/recoveryAgent.ts
Tool Description

The tool analyzes:

academic task list
estimated hours remaining
available hours
due dates
progress percentage
importance
difficulty
energy level
stress level
fixed commitments

It returns structured workload information for the recovery agent.

